<view class="container">
	<view class="title">几何战士</view>
	<view class="subtitle">Web-View 小程序壳</view>

	<view class="label">H5 地址（必须 HTTPS）</view>
	<input
		class="url-input"
		type="text"
		value="{{h5Url}}"
		placeholder="https://cruciata.github.io/Geometry-Survivor/"
		bindinput="onUrlInput"
	/>

	<button class="btn primary" bindtap="saveUrl">保存地址</button>
	<button class="btn" bindtap="openGame">打开游戏</button>

	<view class="tips-title">注意事项</view>
	<view class="tip">1. 小程序仅支持加载 HTTPS 页面</view>
	<view class="tip">2. 该域名需在微信公众平台配置为业务域名</view>
	<view class="tip">3. H5 页面需可在手机浏览器正常访问</view>
</view>
